----------Version-1.3----------
Added bStats.
Better macro list.
Bug fix.

----------Version-1.4----------
Shortcuts added
:) = %smiley%
:( = %sad%
<3 = %heart%

5 new emojis
%sad% = ☹
%hammer-and-sickle% = ☭
%hammer-and-pick% = ⚒
%radioactive% = ☢
%queen% = ♕

----------Version-2.0----------
Now you can use macro on a sign!
Possibility to turn off signs, shortcuts, and metrics.

New perms added:
emoji.list      | to use /emoji list
emoji.chat      | to use macro in chat
emoji.shortcuts | to use shortcuts in chat
emoji.sign      | to use macro on sign

----------Version-2.1----------
More emojis!
Added /help
New perms added:
emoji.help      | to use /emoji help

