----------Version-4.0----------
Long time no see!
A lot of work has been done lately. This plugin is not abandon :D
To use version 4.0 please reinstall the config file. New macros have been added and names have been changed.
----New----
In total, we now have 109 emoji to choose from(/emoji list)!
Added support for 1.15
Bug fix ofc!
You can now choose how many lines to display on /emoji list

----------Version-4.1----------
Some minor changes
We've got discord!
https://discord.gg/rndvHKe
----New----
You can now change the % symbols surrounding the emoji name.
Auto update added.
Api-version updated to 1.15.
Fixed comments in config.

----------Version-4.1.1----------
